<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Privacy Policy - FMPG</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/logo.png" type="image/icon type">
    
    <!-- Central Tailwind CSS & Theme Config -->
    <%- include('tailwind-head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-bg-body text-text-primary min-h-screen flex flex-col transition-colors duration-300">
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include('header') %>

    <!-- Header Banner -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/5 to-transparent border-b border-border-color/60">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center space-y-2">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold font-heading text-primary">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm md:text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">Last updated: May 2026. Review FMPG's data practices, user rights, and information retention guidelines.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Workspace -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start animate-fade-in-up">
            
            <!-- Quick Sidebar Index Navigation -->
            <aside class="md:col-span-4 sticky top-24 bg-bg-card/40 border border-border-color/60 rounded-2xl p-5 space-y-3 hidden md:block">
                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest border-b border-border-color pb-2 mb-3">Policy Index</h4>
                <nav class="space-y-2 text-xs font-semibold text-text-secondary">
                    <a href="#collection" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">1. Personal Info Collection</a>
                    <a href="#usage" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">2. Use of Information</a>
                    <a href="#sharing" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">3. Sharing of Information</a>
                    <a href="#rights" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">4. User Rights & Options</a>
                    <a href="#security" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">5. Data Security Protocols</a>
                    <a href="#cookies" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">6. Cookies & Tracking</a>
                    <a href="#transfers" class="block hover:text-primary transition-colors">7. International Transfers</a>
                </nav>
            </aside>

            <!-- Detailed Policy Blocks -->
            <article class="md:col-span-8 glass-panel rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 border border-border-color shadow-xl space-y-8 font-body text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                
                <!-- Section 1 -->
                <section id="collection" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        1. Personal Information Collection
                    </h2>
                    <p>The platform collects personal information, including name, email, address, phone number, and other identifiers when you register an account, fill forms, or sync reservations.</p>
                    <p>Information may also be collected from social media accounts if linked to the platform. We track analytical data through cookies to enhance functional layouts.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 2 -->
                <section id="usage" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        2. Use of Information
                    </h2>
                    <p>Personal information is utilized specifically to provide, verify, and improve the accommodation booking services, coordinate check-in dates, and execute transactional validations.</p>
                    <p>We may also use data for product updates, security checkups, and necessary communications regarding account status changes.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 3 -->
                <section id="sharing" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        3. Sharing of Information
                    </h2>
                    <p>Personal data may be shared with verified PG Owners (only related checkout info) to confirm check-ins, or secure third-party processing integrations like payment gateways (Razorpay).</p>
                    <p>No details are shared with unverified external agents. Under legally mandated conditions, we may transfer information to government authorities or in mergers/acquisitions.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 4 -->
                <section id="rights" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        4. User Rights & Options
                    </h2>
                    <p>Users maintain complete rights to access, update, correct, or delete their profile information from the database at any time. Simply navigate to settings or submit a request to support.</p>
                    <p>Users are also entitled to withdraw processing consents, which might affect checkout access controls.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 5 -->
                <section id="security" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        5. Data Security Protocols
                    </h2>
                    <p>We execute standard 256-bit encryption protocols to protect data transfers. Users are strictly advised to keep their account passwords confidential as no system guarantees complete virtual security.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 6 -->
                <section id="cookies" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        6. Cookies & Tracking
                    </h2>
                    <p>We deploy tracking cookies, session configurations, and local parameters to persist login choices, detect theme switcher settings (fmpg-theme), and measure traffic flow accurately.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Section 7 -->
                <section id="transfers" class="space-y-3">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-extrabold font-heading text-text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-primary rounded"></span>
                        7. International Transfers
                    </h2>
                    <p>As FMPG serves regional and international tenants, database nodes may process elements in secure cloud containers outside of your home country under strict compliance codes.</p>
                </section>

            </article>

        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('footer') %>
</body>

</html>